! A Sci-Fi Constitution
!!!! 2026-01

Below is a fantasy: a re-factoring and bug-fix of the US Constitution.  It is
as much wish fulfillment as it is science-fiction speculation.  The underlying
sci-fi narrative is that this new-and-revised US Constitution is, by one or
many applications of the current Article 5, sometime in the few years after
2026 ratified.

Scroll down to *Article 0* for the good stuff.  Before then are some
extra-textual remarks.

!!! Style of Changes

The changes are roughly of 5 kinds, which arranged from least to most radical
are:
# {|
# \[
# \begin{align}
