*CALIBRATION OF INJURY* --- Excessive bail shall not be required, nor excessive
fines imposed, nor cruel and unusual punishments inflicted.  Private property
shall not be taken for public use, without just compensation.



*TREASON* --- Treason against the United States shall consist only in levying
war against them, or in adhering to their enemies, giving them aid and comfort.
No person shall be convicted of treason unless on the testimony of two
witnesses to the same overt act, or on confession in open Court.   The Congress
shall have power to declare the punishment of treason, but no attainder of
treason shall work corruption of blood, or forfeiture except during the life of
the person attainted.



